### App Service API Tests
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json
@tenantId = acme-corp
@appId = main-app

### 1. Create App
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tenants/{{tenantId}}/apps
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "id": "main-app",
  "name": "Main Application",
  "type": "web",
  "config": {
    "access_token_expiry": 3600000000000,
    "refresh_token_expiry": 86400000000000,
    "token_algorithm": "HS256"
  }
}

### 2. Get App by ID
# @name getApp
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tenants/{{tenantId}}/apps/{{appId}}

### 3. Get App by Code
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tenants/{{tenantId}}/apps/code/main-app

### 4. List All Apps for Tenant
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tenants/{{tenantId}}/apps

### 5. Update App
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tenants/{{tenantId}}/apps/{{appId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Main Application Updated",
  "description": "Updated primary application",
  "settings": {
    "enable_oauth2": true,
    "enable_api_keys": true,
    "enable_passkey": true
  }
}

### 6. Delete App
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tenants/{{tenantId}}/apps/{{appId}}
